
# Privacy Policy for Climate Canvas


## Introduction

At Climate Canvas, we are committed to respecting the privacy of the users of our Android application. This Privacy Policy outlines the information we collect and how we use that information.

## Information We Collect

Climate Canvas does not collect any personal data. We do not collect, store, or share any data related to your usage of this app.

## Permissions

The app only requests permissions that are absolutely necessary for its functionality. These permissions are used solely for the purpose of providing the app's services and improving your user experience.

## Third-Party Access

We do not share any data with third parties. Since we do not collect user data, there is no data to share.

## Ads

Climate Canvas does not contain any ads. We prioritize your user experience and privacy over ad revenue.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.


## 7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: wycliffepepela@gmail.com
